metadata.description:
The floor is collapsing. The sweeping has stopped. You thought the project would explode, but it ended up being a dud.

People are getting sucked into a pipe-dreams thinking that the project will moon - and that dream has since been shattered. 

But don't fret! Act fast, spend the gas, and navigate this treacherous terrain.

If you can avoid the insanity, slow-moving blockchains and naysayers - you might just get out of this unscathed. 

Just continue rolling on the floor, laughing.
